description:
### Century From Year

Given a year, return its corresponding century. Years end in 00 are considered to be part of the previous century.

Input: An integer within the range of 1 to 2005.
Output: An integer representing the century for the given year.

Example:

``` 
centuryFromYear(2000) // 20
centuryFromYear(2001) // 21
 ```
